  "title": "In Waking Life",
  "description": "WINNER: BEST OF TORONTO FRINGE. The Synsk Sisters are back, Edmonton! Two charming psychics who are here to fix all of your problems (and ignore their own). An award-winning, laugh-out-loud comedy. “Unpredictably funny, ★★★★1/2” -Edmonton Journal. “You’d have to be made of stone not to laugh at this show” -Mooney on Theatre.",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Lauren Welchner &amp; Monica Bradford-Lea<br><strong>Cast</strong>: Lauren Welchner &amp; Monica Bradford-Lea<br/></br>",
  "website": "https://spicyday.ca | @spicy_day",
  "plain_language": "In Waking Life is a hilarious play about two kooky psychic sisters named Cora and Garnish Synsk. The sisters are running a secret psychic business at the Edmonton Fringe Festival, and you, the audience, are their customers. The sisters are excited to help you solve all of your problems, as they struggle to deal with their own.",
